<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?><root available-locales="en_US" default-locale="en_US"><Summary language-id="en_US"><p>Meet Liferay developers and IT professionals to the fifth Liferay DEVCON in Amsterdam! Talk with Liferay engineers from around the world and gain valuable insights for your Liferay projects. Get answers to your questions, learn about new features and use the opportunity to help shape the Liferay community and development in a unique way. You can look forward to a lot of time to exchange knowledge, networking and fun.<br />
&nbsp;<br />
This year we offer on October 4, the day before the DEVCON, a UnConference as a special highlight. Here the participants build the agenda at the beginning in a plenary session. The UnConference offers a special environment for knowledge sharing and targeted exchange with peers.</p>

<p>Seats for DEVCON and Unconference are limited and we expect to be sold out during summer time. Don't miss to register soon at www.liferay,com/devcon2017<br />
&nbsp;<br />
Please also have a look at our recap page 2016 to find out what to expect: wwww.liferay.com/devcon</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p></Summary></root>
